{"tid":1841740,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【人生贏家】愛情事業兩得意 南野拓實認與水着女星熱戀","createTime":"2020-01-25T11:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T11:21:55.000Z","uid":10199,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"80036218bd3586199917b2760e8a33a251ad4649","tid":1841740,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579932104_f234.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579932104_f234.jpg&h=7231d632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n剛在對狼隊一仗入替沙迪奧文尼，首次於英超賽事亮相的25歲利物浦中場南野拓實，已透過事務所證實，正跟身材火辣的25歲日本女星柳百合菜相戀。<br />\n<br />\n寫真偶像出身的百合菜，近年已投身影視界，曾參演多部電視劇，包括在2014年的日劇《阿政－威士忌第一人》飾演小綠一角，她在2018年上映的電影《純平，重新考慮》中更有大膽裸露演出。<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒引述消息人士透露，南野拓實的一名好友，去年底跟百合菜的胞姐結婚，而南野之前有一次回國跟該名好友聚會時認識了百合菜，由於兩人都是來自大阪，所以特別投契，並於去年夏天正式成為情侶。據悉，百合菜上月就特別到過奧地利，跟當時仍然效力薩爾斯堡的南野托實見面。知情者又透露，為免令足球事業如日方中的南野拓實分心，百合菜從來沒有在Twitter或instagram等社交媒體「放閃」，甚至連歐遊的相片也未有發佈。不過，日本傳媒指報道，南野與百合菜的事務所，分別已經低調證實兩人相戀的消息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579933146_c636.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579933146_c636.jpg&h=9f3076b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579932150_4637.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579932150_4637.jpg&h=919d11b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200125/large/1579932142_5626.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200125%2Flarge%2F1579932142_5626.jpg&h=76918e95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73202b3129c0ca0b40f85cf82d118d47b1a31d59","tid":1841740,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"我係足球員呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b1926880b53a5a9a3a0a52547b786560eaaf9a","tid":1841740,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老婆!"}]}